        "endDie": 4,
        "name": "Ethereal Grasp (Magical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Unfettered Familiar extends its ethereal form to touch a target. The target must succeed on an Endurance check or suffer 1 Astral damage and be Blinded for 1 round.</p></div>"
